# mplayer

> Cross-platform multimedia player
> More information: https://mplayerhq.hu/DOCS/HTML/en/commandline.html

- Play the specified file or URL:

`mplayer {string value: path/to/file|url}`

- Play multiple files:

`mplayer {file* value}`

- Play a specific file repeatedly:

`mplayer -loop {int value: 0} {file value}`

- Pause playback:

`<Space>`

- Quit mplayer:

`<Escape>`

- Seek backward or forward 10 seconds:

`<Left> or <Right>`
